title: Green tomato cake
ingredients: ['725g chopped green tomatoes', '1 tablespoon salt', '125g butter', '400g caster sugar', '2 eggs', '250g plain flour', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1 teaspoon ground nutmeg', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1/4 teaspoon salt', '60g sultanas or raisins', '60g chopped walnuts']
